    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i> 2) They land on your custom page.</strong>
      <div>Your catalog appears instantly — branded for your show.</div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i> 3) They find the song.</strong>
      <div>Search, browse, or manually enter a title you don't have yet.</div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i> 4) They submit their request.</strong>
      <div>It jumps straight into your rotation with their name.</div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-list-check"></i> 5) You manage the queue effortlessly.</strong>
      <div>Automated rotation logic keeps everything fair — no line cutters, no repeats, no arguing (but YOU can still adjust if needed).</div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-bell"></i> 6) The singer sees exactly where they stand.</strong>
      <div>Personal page updates live. Push alerts hit when they're up next and when it's time to sing. No more "AM I NEXT?!" shouted from across the room.</div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong><i class="fa-solid fa-face-smile"></i> 7) Happy singers. Smooth rotation. Zero paper.</strong>
      <div>Your night feels professional, modern, and stress-free.</div>
    </li>
  </ol>
  <div class="landing-cta-block">
    <h3>Ready to Ditch Paper Slips for Good?</h3>
    <p><a href="<%= signup_path %>" role="button">Get Started</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="landing-divider">

<%# ── Feature Grid ── %>
<section class="container landing-section">
  <header style="text-align: center;">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles"></i> Everything You Need for a Smooth, Stress-Free Karaoke Night</h2>
  </header>
